_sText:
This is a gun-game map made for an average of about 5-10 people at max, but for the more big servers, I have put in about 18 spawns at each team, equaling to be 36 spawns in total.

Secrets (SPOILER ALERT): There is one secret at the yellow box. if you go to the side of the yellow box, then press your "use" button (usually "e") the box will open. You must jump a pretty easy fall, then go down the hallway, you will then be teleported to a balcony (as shown in picture three above).
